title: King Canopy Universal Canopy 10-Feet by 27-Feet, 1 3/8-Inch Steel Frame, 10 Leg, Quick Shade, Camping, Boat Shelter, Events, Party Tent, Carport, White, C81027PC

Replacement Parts: King Canopy has replacement parts on hand and ready to ship.
Trained Customer Serivce: Our customer support staff has been trained with our full line of products and will be able to assist you with any questions or concerns you may have about our products.
description: The Universal line of King Canopies are great for everyday use. This 10 by 27 is great to cover your vehicle, boat and trailer. Use at a family function for a covered gathering.
